Founders | Josiah & McKenna Datria

Josie's Coffee Co. was created out of a husband's desire to craft him and his wife great coffee every morning. With that same heart, our hope is to serve that same high quality coffee to the community around us! Our goal is create specialty coffee the fun way, bringing unforgettable experiences wherever we serve.
